            f"- кіөмһҘ: мғқм„ұ {FACTORY_V299_STATS.get('factory_build',0)}нҡҢ / мһ¬мӮ¬мҡ© {FACTORY_V299_STATS.get('factory_reuse',0)}нҡҢ / мғқм„ұмӨ‘ мһ¬мӮ¬мҡ© {FACTORY_V299_STATS.get('factory_busy_reuse',0)}нҡҢ / мөңк·ј {safe_float(FACTORY_V299_STATS.get('last_factory_sec',0),0):.2f}s",
            f"- row: л№ лҘён–ү {FACTORY_V299_STATS.get('fast_row',0)}к°ң / fallback {FACTORY_V299_STATS.get('fallback_row',0)}к°ң / нҸүк·  {avg_ms:.2f}ms",
            f"- мөңк·ј л©”лӘЁ: {FACTORY_V299_STATS.get('last_factory_note','-')}",
