        f"- мһ¬к°җмӢң м°ЁлӢЁ: л¬ҙл„Ҳм§җ {V317_STATS.get('reroute_blocked_dead',0)} / м•Ҫн•Ё {V317_STATS.get('reroute_blocked_weak',0)} / л°ҳліө {V317_STATS.get('reroute_blocked_repeat',0)}",
        f"- мөңк·ј6h: мІӯмӮ° {closed_n} / м·ЁмҶҢ {cancel_n} / л¬¶мқҖлҶ“м№Ё {missed_n} / лҲ„м Ғ {total:+.2f}% / PF {pf:.2f}",
        f"- version tag: мІӯмӮ° {V317_STATS.get('version_tag_close',0)} / м·ЁмҶҢ {V317_STATS.get('version_tag_cancel',0)}",
